      • compareAttributeWith

        public java.util.List<Regiao> compareAttributeWith(java.lang.String regionAttribute,
                                                   java.lang.String relationalOperator,
                                                   java.lang.String toCompareAttribute)

        Method that compares the values of the operands

        For each region in regioes the method will test if the value of the region field corresponding to the first operand is equal the value of the region field corresponding to the second operand

        Second operand is always an Attribute

        Parameters:
        regionAttribute - - Operand 1 of condition
        relationalOperator - - Condition Operator
        toCompareAttribute - - Operand 2 of condition - Is an Attribute
        Returns:
        - List containing the regions that matches the condition
